<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4676708>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Myopsalta atrata—illustration of male pygofer and internal genitalia;(A) viewed laterally from the left;(B) viewed ventrally;(C) aedeagus, lateral view; and (D) aedeagus, rotated 30° left from central view C. Characters include:aed, aedeagus; as, anal style; bpl, basal lobe of pygofer; cl, clasper;db, dorsal beak;eth, endotheca;ps, pseudoparameres;un, uncus;upl, upper lobe of pygofer;vs, ventral support." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4676708/files/figure.png" .

